SuggestionBox
=============

SuggestionBox Helper.  For Partner Fusion use only.


Example
=======

Make sure you have the config file 'suggestion_box.yml' in your config folder:

# config/suggestion_box.yml
--- 
  :url: url_to_suggesion_box (including http/https)
  
  
# app/layouts/application.html.erb (before </body> tag)
<%= suggestion_box('my_application_name') %>


